snippet: Serena Williams won her 750th career match to stay on track for her ninth Miami Open title when she beat Zarina Diyas of Kazakhstan 7-5 6-3 in the third round in Florida on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams won her 750th career match to stay on track for her ninth Miami Open title when she beat Zarina Diyas of Kazakhstan 7-5 6-3 in the third round in Florida on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Serena Williams Takes Another Step to Ninth Miami Title
headline.main: Serena Williams Takes Another Step to Ninth Miami Title
